data.title: Tanker Association
data.text:
Airlift/Tanker Association

Our system indicates that you are using Internet Explorer.

Unfortunately, you will NOT be able to register for A/TA Convention using the Internet Explorer (IE) browser. Internet Explorer is integral to older Windows platforms and, because those platforms are sunsetting, Microsoft no longer provides maintenance updates for the IE browser rendering it incompatible with our modern site.

We encourage you to register/complete your registration using another browser (Safari, Edge, Firefox, Chrome) or even on your smartphone or tablet.

If none of these options work, please contact us directly for help by email at ata@atalink.org or by phone at (423) 902-2297.
